			<h1>Thanks to CoinMarketCap for the Bitcoin data!</h1>
			<br></br>

			<h3>Predicting the future price of bitcoin with a Long Short Term Memory(LSTM) and time series!</h3>

			<br>

			<div class="card image-card">
				<h5 class="card-title">Bitcoin closing price(UTC time) chart, training set(blue), validation set(green), test set(red)</h5>
				<img src="/images/training-valid-test.png" class="rounded image">
				<h5 class="card-title">Starting from April 29, 2013 to June 30, 2022</h5>
			</div>

			<br><br>

			<div class="card image-card">
				<h5 class="card-title">LSTM model's test set performance.  Model predictions vs actual closing prices.</h5>
				<img src="/images/predicted-vs-actual.png" class="rounded image">
				<h5 class="card-title">Test set starts from January 31, 2022 to June 30, 2022</h5>
			</div>

			<br><br>

			<div class="card image-card">
				<h5 class="card-title">Percentage error in model's test set performance</h5>
				<img src="/images/percent-error.png" class="rounded image">
				<h5 class="card-title">Test set starts from January 31, 2022 to June 30, 2022</h5>
			</div>

			<br><br>

